articles.title: CALENDAR OF EVENTS
articles.summary: This document outlines the San Jose Astronomical Association's upcoming events for September and October, featuring general meetings with lectures, board meetings, and various star parties including an AAVSO/NASA joint conference. It also provides "news notz" with reports on recent observing activities, a thank you to a guest speaker, and brief astronomy news items.

articles.title: A D S  I N F I N I T U M
articles.summary: This document is a classified advertisement listing a Criterion 6" RV6 Dynascope telescope for sale. Priced at $215, the f/8 telescope is described as being in excellent condition and includes three eyepieces, with contact information provided for Doug Buettner.

articles.title: SAN JOSE ASTRONOMICAL ASSOCIATION, INC - SEPTEMBER 1977
articles.summary: This document is a membership roster for the San Jose Astronomical Association, Inc. from September 1977. It lists members' names, addresses, cities, ZIP codes, and phone numbers, serving as a contact directory for the organization.
